Login with email and password.

Response:
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "access_token": "1|abcdef...",
    "token_type": "Bearer",
    "user": {...}
  }
}

Token automatically saved to {{token}} variable.

UPDATED: Response now includes:
- contact_info object with normalized phone and email
- @deprecated object with old fields (nomor_telepon, nomor_telepon_publik)
- Warning header for deprecated fields
- tonase_sampah EXCLUDED from list (performance optimization)

New Response Format:
{
  "success": true,
  "data": [{
    "id": 1,
    "nama_bank_sampah": "Bank Sampah Melati",
    "contact_info": {
      "phone": "081234567890",
      "email": "melati@example.com"
    },
    "@deprecated": {
      "nomor_telepon": "081234567890",
      "nomor_telepon_publik": "081234567890"
    }
  }]
}

